phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common UI test mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| No setContent | Set content |
| No assertions | Add assertions |
| Slow tests | Use mocks |
| Flaky tests | Use waitForIdle |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Set content
composeTestRule.setContent {
    MyScreen()
}

// 2. Add assertions
onNodeWithText("Hello").assertExists()

// 3. Use mocks
val viewModel = mockk<MyViewModel>()

// 4. Wait for conditions
composeTestRule.waitForIdle()

// 5. Cleanup
@After
fun cleanup() {
    // Cleanup code
}
```
